text:
Cannabis Hyperemesis Syndrome.
This shit sucks!! My wife has been trying to figure out why her morning sickness from her last pregnancy never went away and got worse afterwards for 2 1/2 years. None of the Drs had any idea why, it took 5 or 6 hospitalizations before they finally figured out it was CHS. Now she has to stop cold turkey after 20 years, I'm quitting too to help but it's not the same for me, she uses it to medically treat several other conditions where cannabis helps but medications don't. So now it's back to the drawing board on a lot of health stuff for us. But at least we have an answer about the hyperemesis. And thank Goddess she hasn't had a kidney failure or something yet, read how bad CHS can get if not treated. I believe it, it's horrible, she was convinced she was dying.
Sorry just venting a bit but also sharing with /marijuana-family because at first I thought the Drs were just anti-pot. Anyone know someone with this?
https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cannabinoid_hyperemesis_syndrome

text:
This interview with Grayzone reporter Kit Klarenberg is wild af, helped me understand the situation with not just Ukraine and Russia but the US and the world too. 
Western imperialists are headed for nuclear war and maybe no one can stop it. There's no logical endgame  but nuclear war and annihilation. There's no other strategy.
I want humanity to rise up! Human beings are capable of love and beautiful society. We can move beyond war. But how? I hate just waiting for the world war I don't want to happen at all but it doesn't seem that any political organizing makes a difference at all. But I think our power has to be in uniting all of humanity that wants peace. Which again leads me back to crypto values, so we have a starting point, but how can we organize all humanity to build a whole new system? That's our #1 political question now but if we answer it before the collapse they'll take us out. ü§∑‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è
